{"tid":2175437,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"從前以為係黑白良知問題，發現其實係認知問題","createTime":"2020-08-26T12:51:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-26T13:00:37.000Z","uid":81236,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"aaa2f880289c66277a4280c8717bc4470e42581f","tid":2175437,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T12:51:52.000Z","msg":"對於顛倒是非黑呢方面<br />\n<br />\n將錯既事講成岩，從來都知係強項<br />\n<br />\n但原來可以指鹿為馬、篡改歷史<br />\n<br />\n兩樣有根本性差別<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黑白良知係對一件事上既理性回應<br />\n<br />\n而指鹿為馬係根本上改變事件客觀性質同認知<br />\n<br />\n篡改歷史就更加唔洗講<br />\n<br />\n從前覺得係黑白良知問題<br />\n<br />\n但原來有既係認知問題<br />\n<br />\n就好似曼德拉效應咁，好多事只係世人錯誤認知<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當知道係認知問題後，終於令世人了解真相<br />\n<br />\n721及暴動係由林卓延帶起、白衣人保家衛國<br />\n<br />\n831係警察係地鐵無差別救人<br />\n<br />\n8964無死過人<br />\n<br />\n香港警察係嚴正執法最好的<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其餘更多真相有待公布<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef8e8945ce369097dc4ca2a342f4d5c05c928c1f","tid":2175437,"uid":9193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T12:52:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b109d24f6b6fbd0cf5132e2abe07550cadb49065","tid":2175437,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T12:54:47.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係香港人有認知問題"},{"pid":"cec8668144245986eba67420969c1f51fa6b64b3","tid":2175437,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T12:56:20.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"266ea833ed5a4d0f51ce35133356d1b783934a7e","tid":2175437,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T13:00:37.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}